issue.title: Changed @NotNull to Validate.notNull() in Aether.jara
issue.body: This PR is for issue #78 . Build under openjdk6 (and oraclejdk6) fails when `javax.validation.constraints.@NotNull` is used for validation, so I used `org.apache.commons.lang3.Validate.notNull()` instead.
